  "title": "Locum Occupational Therapist (Senior Care Centre & Nursing Home, Macpherson/Paya Lebar)",
  "description": "<p>We are actively hiring for a client in a Senior Care Centre & Nursing Home setting in Singapore and we wish to invite interested therapists to apply the role.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Code: SNHC22/12/OT</strong></p><p><strong>Locum Occupational Therapist - 6 months contract</strong></p><ul><li>Assess patients' physical, emotional, and cognitive challenges.</li><li>Develop and implement customized therapy programs to enhance daily functioning.</li><li>Teach patients adaptive techniques and recommend assistive devices.</li><li>Work with families and caregivers to support patient rehabilitation.</li><li>Modify environments (home, school, or workplace) to improve accessibility and safety.</li><li>Collaborate with healthcare professionals, including physiotherapists and doctors.</li><li>Monitor progress and adjust treatment plans accordingly.</li></ul><p><strong>Project Details</strong></p><ul><li>3 days per week, 9am - 4pm</li><li>Projected Commencement: from early January 2026 onwards</li><li>Competitive hourly remuneration covered with Medical Malpractice + Complimentary access to CPE events conducted by Pacific Rehab Group</li><li>Bachelor or Masters in Occupational Therapy</li><li>Must be a Fully Registered AHPC ( Singapore )</li><li>Senior therapists are welcome to apply</li></ul><p><strong>Drop in your CV to: hr@pacificrehab.com.sg</strong></p><p><strong>Or WhatsApp 8022 6814</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Quick SIGN UP here : https://form.jotform.com/250558451726461</strong></p>",
